description.narrative:
"The assignment involves assessment of the current and future landscape of Government policy making and R&I excellence in India with focus on the following:
1. Government of India R&I priorities – including a snapshot of the system.
2. Where excellence currently lies in relation to current GoI priorities;
3. Which State Governments will play a prominent role in the implementation of these priorities;
4. Which academic institutions, incubators and think-tanks are supporting the development of GoI’s vision (including, but not limited to, GoI funded labs and institutions);
5. Which academic institutions, incubators and think-tanks will support the development of GoI’s vision over the next 3, 5 and 10 years;
6. Analysis of trends in terms of scientific output across regions/locations/institutes."
